{"tid":1167629,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他們曾說過……","createTime":"2019-05-23T07:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T08:04:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da36152e116d37c749df5cea1288ddb7b948bad9","tid":1167629,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190523/20685000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F20685000&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1UoyozY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=afb574bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F20685000&h=485a7e4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190523/20685000</a><br />\n<br />\n他們曾說過&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190523/large/1630587.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190523%2Flarge%2F1630587.jpg&h=54073ca3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁振英<br />\n<br />\n我當時一方面感到震驚，因為一直以來對嗰場學生運動，都感覺到係相當和平嘅一場運動，我覺得冇咁嘅需要。亦都感覺到有啲迷惑李鵬總理喺學生已經宣佈咗話要停止絕食、撤出天安門嘅時候，仲有一個咁樣嘅決定。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府喺事前作嘅承諾，後來都一一落空，包括不秋後算賬，包括軍隊唔係用來對付學生呢啲承諾，後來都落空咗。香港嘅未來同中國政府畀香港嘅承諾，無論係中英聯合聲明裏面嘅承諾、基本法裏面嘅承諾，係有好密切嘅關係，如果中國政府係咁唔重視自己嘅承諾嘅話，係好難怪香港人對中國政府失咗信心嘅。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;1988年起出任基本法諮詢委員會秘書長的梁振英，六四事件後接受電視台訪問，評論中共中央1989年5月派駐解放軍進入北京，及六四後秋後算賬大規模逮捕參與民運的人士。  <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：開page回帶 認識歷史無分世代<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n恐共黨滲透變六七翻版 三罷叫停<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n蘋人誌：前世或是西藏人 今生只做香港人薯伯伯<br />\n<br />\n開page回帶 認識歷史無分世代<br />\n恐共黨滲透變六七翻版 三罷叫停<br />\n六四30年：經歷八九世代懺悔：我們做少了"},{"pid":"d02ff409de095c5986f12ff96a9d96f660dee168","tid":1167629,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T07:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e70faf812e75ba145524aea1a79afde8afabc1","tid":1167629,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"咩時勢就講咩說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0469b6ddad18ff94328f69127f64e3e9592804","tid":1167629,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T08:04:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">國家領導人<strong>梁振英</strong>同志</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wemedia01-prod.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media/images/112925/org/a1b1ff5e103561df86192f45fa121aa5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwemedia01-prod.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F112925%2Forg%2Fa1b1ff5e103561df86192f45fa121aa5.gif&h=75000719&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}